ewu.embroidit.parkc.io

Class FormatPES

  • java.lang.Object
    • ewu.embroidit.parkc.io.FormatPES

  • public class FormatPES
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class opens a .PES file and interprets the stitch data extracted by the PECDecoder class. This data is used to create the stitches for an embroidery pattern.
